1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:04,000
 Hvala si, Marija, svima.

2
00:00:04,000 --> 00:00:08,000
 Evo, počet ću jednim događajem, ne znam točno,

3
00:00:08,000 --> 00:00:13,000
 koje godine, čini se 2013. godine,

4
00:00:13,000 --> 00:00:21,000
 u Vitezi su dolazili grupa, neki, evo, karizmatici, recimo.

5
00:00:21,000 --> 00:00:26,000
 Ja sam tad i isto bio svećenik, pa on sam počeo tih stvarmano boljaživo raditi.

6
00:00:26,000 --> 00:00:30,000
 I budući da tamo župnik nije dao u crkvi da se održi,

7
00:00:30,000 --> 00:00:35,000
 valjda, dobri pastir, ti seminer, onaj je bio u tamo nekom hotelu,

8
00:00:35,000 --> 00:00:39,000
 vi koji se izvitali za to znate, i ja sam tako bio tu,

9
00:00:39,000 --> 00:00:43,000
 i posle moli smo gore ovako na Bini,

10
00:00:43,000 --> 00:00:47,000
 i onda pituje mene, ćeš i ti otići da mole za tebe,

11
00:00:47,000 --> 00:00:49,000
 ti lajici, ko ću, nemoj se.

12
00:00:49,000 --> 00:00:52,000
 Ja sam otišao, tako se malo pomoli.

13
00:00:52,000 --> 00:00:56,000
 Neko tih muškaraca, kare, fra Jospe,

14
00:00:56,000 --> 00:01:00,000
 a u stvari bio sam možda čak i u civilu, nisam siguran,

15
00:01:00,000 --> 00:01:01,000
 kaže: "Vidim te,

16
00:01:01,000 --> 00:01:04,000
 idi, odazove se Bog te zove,

17
00:01:04,000 --> 00:01:06,000
 ićeš propovijati evanđelje,

18
00:01:06,000 --> 00:01:08,000
 masama svijeta, ićeš po svijetu."

19
00:01:08,000 --> 00:01:11,000
 Ja godam njega, čudim se jako malo,

20
00:01:11,000 --> 00:01:16,000
 poko Bog fala, i tako to se završio, ja se vratio na svoje mjesto,

21
00:01:16,000 --> 00:01:21,000
 i odmah poslje toga počeli se te stvari događati,

22
00:01:21,000 --> 00:01:25,000
 da su ljudi počeli pozivati na razgovore, na susrete,

23
00:01:25,000 --> 00:01:30,000
 da držim duhovne obnove, i tako je to krenulo i preko Međugorje još ranije,

24
00:01:30,000 --> 00:01:36,000
 ali to sam nekako sebe i vidio kao ispovednika u Međugorju,

25
00:01:36,000 --> 00:01:39,000
 pa mnogi od vas i poznajem da li sam im susreo,

26
00:01:39,000 --> 00:01:42,000
 ali da ću držati kao neka predavanja, seminare,

27
00:01:42,000 --> 00:01:45,000
 ili tako ići po svijetu, to nisam ni sanjao.

28
00:01:45,000 --> 00:01:47,000
 Međutim, eto, to se ostvarilo,

29
00:01:47,000 --> 00:01:50,000
 i sad kad razgradamo ovde puna crkva,

30
00:01:50,000 --> 00:01:53,000
 i na drugim mjestima, kako je to lijepo biti,

31
00:01:53,000 --> 00:01:56,000
 još baš u crkvi, ne u hotelu,

32
00:01:56,000 --> 00:01:59,000
 kod ovdje nemamo, baš ovdje u crkvi Sv. Petra,

33
00:01:59,000 --> 00:02:03,000
 i Pavla, i baš kod fratara.

34
00:02:03,000 --> 00:02:16,000
 A onda da mi je neko govorio da ću držati jednu knjigu o duhu svijetu,

35
00:02:16,000 --> 00:02:19,000
 za par godina ne bi ni to ni ka sanjao.

36
00:02:19,000 --> 00:02:22,000
 Evo i to je isto bio Boži poticaj,

37
00:02:22,000 --> 00:02:26,000
 u našoj provinciji je bila neka smjena uredništva svijeta riječi,

38
00:02:26,000 --> 00:02:30,000
 i onda je falo tih ljudi koji će sada uđi uskočiti,

39
00:02:30,000 --> 00:02:32,000
 to znate kad su promjene.

40
00:02:32,000 --> 00:02:34,000
 I mene je uhvatio jedan iz uprave,

41
00:02:34,000 --> 00:02:38,000
 sad vremena me lomio, ajde uđi tamo uredništva,

42
00:02:38,000 --> 00:02:41,000
 šta ne pišem, ne mogu ja, nisam, zato ja ću spovijeti,

43
00:02:41,000 --> 00:02:44,000
 moraš tamo ideti poslušanost bila.

44
00:02:44,000 --> 00:02:46,000
 I ja sam, on me je rekao, ajde makar jedan,

45
00:02:46,000 --> 00:02:49,000
 dva članka da napišem, se objave sjetno riječ preko ljeta,

46
00:02:49,000 --> 00:02:51,000
 da ne bi bilo nekog zastoja.

47
00:02:51,000 --> 00:02:57,000
 zastoja, ja sam to poslušao i napisao sam članak kriza vjere,

48
00:02:57,000 --> 00:03:01,000
 kriza zvanja, zapravo duhovnih sam tamo odgojite u Svjemeništu,

49
00:03:01,000 --> 00:03:03,000
 pa to znam u čemu se radi.

50
00:03:03,000 --> 00:03:07,000
 Kad sljedeći put, kad još jedan članak, još jedan veće,

51
00:03:07,000 --> 00:03:09,000
 to je bilo 7-8 mjesec,

52
00:03:09,000 --> 00:03:12,000
 vidim ja, oni traže, šta ću sada?

53
00:03:12,000 --> 00:03:14,000
 Na ovoga sam izmišlja teme,

54
00:03:14,000 --> 00:03:17,000
 onda mi pade na pamet, idem pisati o Duhu Svjeta,

55
00:03:17,000 --> 00:03:20,000
 jer to nije baš skoro niko pisao u Svetu riječ,

56
00:03:20,000 --> 00:03:22,000
 ponekad bude neki članak.

57
00:03:22,000 --> 00:03:24,000
 I onda sam ja uzeo pisa te članke,

58
00:03:24,000 --> 00:03:27,000
 a vi znate koji pišete za novne,

59
00:03:27,000 --> 00:03:29,000
 kako je to uvijek nekako knap vrijeme,

60
00:03:29,000 --> 00:03:32,000
 dođe 15. mjesecu i moraš članak napisati

61
00:03:32,000 --> 00:03:35,000
 ili budete određeno jedna stranca.

62
00:03:35,000 --> 00:03:38,000
 I ja sam onda krenuo, idem pisati o Duhu Svjeta,

63
00:03:38,000 --> 00:03:39,000
 ajde znam, daro je Duha Svjeta,

64
00:03:39,000 --> 00:03:42,000
 to ću pisati, malo pa onda karizme, pa plodove,

65
00:03:42,000 --> 00:03:44,000
 i tako, malo pa malo,

66
00:03:44,000 --> 00:03:47,000
 kroz te članke, kroz tih šest godina

67
00:03:47,000 --> 00:03:51,000
 koliko sam pisao, stvorila se jedna knjiga,

68
00:03:51,000 --> 00:03:53,000
 i evo, Duh Svjeta je to sve vodio,

69
00:03:53,000 --> 00:03:55,000
 nisam ni sanju, nisam ni planirao,

70
00:03:55,000 --> 00:03:58,000
 a evo, najavljujem, bit će još koja knjiga pišem,

71
00:03:58,000 --> 00:03:59,000
 da se to riječi.

72
00:03:59,000 --> 00:04:03,000
 Evo, hvala Bogu da je to izašlo,

73
00:04:03,000 --> 00:04:05,000
 i nadam se da će ova knjiga,

74
00:04:05,000 --> 00:04:06,000
 ja to ja ne smijer baš reklamirati,

75
00:04:06,000 --> 00:04:08,000
 vi ćete, kad budete čitali, gledati.

76
00:04:08,000 --> 00:04:10,000
 To su, uglavnom, tuđe misli,

77
00:04:10,000 --> 00:04:12,000
 ja sam to čitao, gledao,

78
00:04:12,000 --> 00:04:15,000
 praučavao, pisao na brzinu,

79
00:04:15,000 --> 00:04:18,000
 tako, ono, uvijek, zbog ovih drugih potreba,

80
00:04:18,000 --> 00:04:21,000
 jer sam vodio duhovno-pastorni centar,

81
00:04:21,000 --> 00:04:23,000
 ljudi dolaze neispojeni i tako,

82
00:04:23,000 --> 00:04:24,000
 nema puno vremena za pisanje,

83
00:04:24,000 --> 00:04:27,000
 ali sam ipak, evo, to uradio,

84
00:04:27,000 --> 00:04:30,000
 i zafejući suradnicima koji su mi pomogli,

85
00:04:30,000 --> 00:04:32,000
 taj je knjiga ugledala svjeto dana,

86
00:04:32,000 --> 00:04:34,000
 znači, dah duha,

87
00:04:34,000 --> 00:04:36,000
 duha, duha svjeti,

88
00:04:36,000 --> 00:04:39,000
 da je dah, dah života, dah,

89
00:04:39,000 --> 00:04:41,000
 znači, neki lagani povjetarac.

90
00:04:41,000 --> 00:04:45,000
 Pa evo, što bi iz te knjige ovako izvojio,

91
00:04:45,000 --> 00:04:48,000
 što je za nas ovde možda važno,

92
00:04:48,000 --> 00:04:51,000
 kako sam ja to malo otkrio,

93
00:04:51,000 --> 00:04:53,000
 da postoje darovi Božji,

94
00:04:53,000 --> 00:04:55,000
 ne samo duha svjetoga,

95
00:04:55,000 --> 00:04:57,000
 darovi presvjetog trujstva,

96
00:04:57,000 --> 00:04:59,000
 ovih Bog dijeli zajedno.

97
00:04:59,000 --> 00:05:02,000
 Kad stvara svijest, stvara, kaže otac stvortelj,

98
00:05:02,000 --> 00:05:05,000
 po sinu, u duhu svjetu.

99
00:05:05,000 --> 00:05:07,000
 Uvijek su se trujca zajedno,

100
00:05:07,000 --> 00:05:09,000
 uvijek ekipa zajedno radi,

101
00:05:09,000 --> 00:05:11,000
 otac, sin, duh svjeti,

102
00:05:11,000 --> 00:05:12,000
 i kada je,

103
00:05:12,000 --> 00:05:14,000
 Isus pašava sinicu otkruptelj,

104
00:05:14,000 --> 00:05:16,000
 opet to radi,

105
00:05:16,000 --> 00:05:18,000
 jer je otac straži,

106
00:05:18,000 --> 00:05:20,000
 duh svjeti ga nadaklje i tako dalje,

107
00:05:20,000 --> 00:05:22,000
 i duh svjeti kada dolazi,

108
00:05:22,000 --> 00:05:24,000
 dolazi zato što ga šalju otac i sin,

109
00:05:24,000 --> 00:05:26,000
 znači, sve zajedno,

110
00:05:26,000 --> 00:05:27,000
 presvjetog trujstva.

111
00:05:27,000 --> 00:05:29,000
 I onda, kad se uzmu ti darovi,

112
00:05:29,000 --> 00:05:30,000
 što je svjeti Pavel,

113
00:05:30,000 --> 00:05:32,000
 u poslanci Korinčijanima,

114
00:05:32,000 --> 00:05:33,000
 on kad kaže,

115
00:05:33,000 --> 00:05:35,000
 Bog, misli sam Bog otac,

116
00:05:35,000 --> 00:05:36,000
 gospodin Isusa,

117
00:05:36,000 --> 00:05:37,000
 duh svjeti, duh svjeti,

118
00:05:37,000 --> 00:05:40,000
 kaže da daje otac darove.

119
00:05:40,000 --> 00:05:43,000
 Ima nabrojenih u Rimjanima

120
00:05:43,000 --> 00:05:45,000
 sedam darova,

121
00:05:45,000 --> 00:05:47,000
 to su kao darovi poticaja,

122
00:05:47,000 --> 00:05:49,000
 darovi, recimo,

123
00:05:49,000 --> 00:05:51,000
 da neko bude lider,

124
00:05:51,000 --> 00:05:52,000
 da vodi,

125
00:05:52,000 --> 00:05:53,000
 da služi,

126
00:05:53,000 --> 00:05:54,000
 da reži i tako,

127
00:05:54,000 --> 00:05:56,000
 da radi u kartasu.

128
00:05:56,000 --> 00:05:57,000
 To ste vi ovdje pročite,

129
00:05:57,000 --> 00:05:59,000
 to je meni isto bilo kao jedno otkriće.

130
00:05:59,000 --> 00:06:02,000
 I kaže od tih sedam darova,

131
00:06:02,000 --> 00:06:06,000
 čovjek uglavnom savrši jedan dobro,

132
00:06:06,000 --> 00:06:07,000
 može i dva,

133
00:06:07,000 --> 00:06:09,000
 a one i ostale ne može.

134
00:06:09,000 --> 00:06:11,000
 čovjek može reti po ratu kartasu,

135
00:06:11,000 --> 00:06:12,000
 dobro,

136
00:06:12,000 --> 00:06:14,000
 biti dobar imati,

137
00:06:14,000 --> 00:06:16,000
 ili rati u bolicima,

138
00:06:16,000 --> 00:06:17,000
 sućuti,

139
00:06:17,000 --> 00:06:18,000
 milosređa.

140
00:06:18,000 --> 00:06:20,000
 Ali onda ne može druge posle

141
00:06:20,000 --> 00:06:22,000
 toliko obavljati profesionalni

142
00:06:22,000 --> 00:06:24,000
 ili u duhu ili jako si

143
00:06:24,000 --> 00:06:25,000
 kao taj posao.

144
00:06:25,000 --> 00:06:26,000
 E tako,

145
00:06:26,000 --> 00:06:28,000
 to su dakle darovi Otca Nebeskoga

146
00:06:28,000 --> 00:06:30,000
 koje on nama usadio u stvaranju

147
00:06:30,000 --> 00:06:31,000
 kao klice,

148
00:06:31,000 --> 00:06:33,000
 koje se trebaju razvijati.

149
00:06:33,000 --> 00:06:34,000
 Vi to trebate prepoznat

150
00:06:34,000 --> 00:06:35,000
 kao svoje djece,

151
00:06:35,000 --> 00:06:38,000
 te skonosti za pjevanje,

152
00:06:38,000 --> 00:06:39,000
 slikanje,

153
00:06:39,000 --> 00:06:40,000
 crtanje,

154
00:06:40,000 --> 00:06:41,000
 za sport,

155
00:06:41,000 --> 00:06:42,000
 gimnastiku,

156
00:06:42,000 --> 00:06:43,000
 komunikaciju

157
00:06:43,000 --> 00:06:44,000
 i te darove

158
00:06:44,000 --> 00:06:45,000
 kod djeteta

159
00:06:45,000 --> 00:06:46,000
 razvijati.

160
00:06:46,000 --> 00:06:48,000
 Ne ubijati djete u pojam,

161
00:06:48,000 --> 00:06:49,000
 reći ništa,

162
00:06:49,000 --> 00:06:50,000
 neće biti od tebe.

163
00:06:50,000 --> 00:06:51,000
 Svi imamo te darove

164
00:06:51,000 --> 00:06:52,000
 i treba se razvijati.

165
00:06:52,000 --> 00:06:53,000
 E to su darovi

166
00:06:53,000 --> 00:06:55,000
 kao motivacije,

167
00:06:55,000 --> 00:06:56,000
 poticanja.

168
00:06:56,000 --> 00:06:57,000
 I oni su važni

169
00:06:57,000 --> 00:06:58,000
 za izranju crkve.

170
00:06:58,000 --> 00:07:00,000
 A onda imamo darove

171
00:07:00,000 --> 00:07:01,000
 koje nam daje

172
00:07:01,000 --> 00:07:02,000
 Sin,

173
00:07:02,000 --> 00:07:03,000
 Gospodin Isus Hrist,

174
00:07:03,000 --> 00:07:04,000
 a to su darovi

175
00:07:04,000 --> 00:07:05,000
 za služenje u crkvi.

176
00:07:06,000 --> 00:07:07,000
 evanjelisti,

177
00:07:07,000 --> 00:07:08,000
 apostoli,

178
00:07:08,000 --> 00:07:09,000
 proroci,

179
00:07:09,000 --> 00:07:10,000
 pastiri,

180
00:07:10,000 --> 00:07:11,000
 o tome danas

181
00:07:11,000 --> 00:07:12,000
 se svelo

182
00:07:12,000 --> 00:07:13,000
 na ove tri službe,

183
00:07:13,000 --> 00:07:14,000
 znači,

184
00:07:14,000 --> 00:07:15,000
 džakoni,

185
00:07:15,000 --> 00:07:16,000
 predbitel,

186
00:07:16,000 --> 00:07:17,000
 svećenici

187
00:07:17,000 --> 00:07:18,000
 i biskupi.

188
00:07:18,000 --> 00:07:19,000
 Oni su,

189
00:07:19,000 --> 00:07:20,000
 to su darovi

190
00:07:20,000 --> 00:07:21,000
 za služenje

191
00:07:21,000 --> 00:07:22,000
 u crkvi.

192
00:07:22,000 --> 00:07:23,000
 hierarhijski darovi,

193
00:07:23,000 --> 00:07:25,000
 darovi koji služi crkvi.

194
00:07:25,000 --> 00:07:27,000
 I onda imamo darove

195
00:07:27,000 --> 00:07:28,000
 duha svetoga,

196
00:07:28,000 --> 00:07:30,000
 redovne i varene,

197
00:07:30,000 --> 00:07:32,000
 duha sveti puše gdje hoće

198
00:07:32,000 --> 00:07:34,000
 i daje i te vanredne darove

199
00:07:34,000 --> 00:07:35,000
 o tome u knjizi piše,

200
00:07:35,000 --> 00:07:37,000
 o tome se sada i zove

201
00:07:37,000 --> 00:07:38,000
 karizmanski pokrit.

202
00:07:38,000 --> 00:07:39,000
 Vidjet ćete,

203
00:07:39,000 --> 00:07:41,000
 ja sam nešto u knjizi

204
00:07:41,000 --> 00:07:42,000
 pokušao malo,

205
00:07:42,000 --> 00:07:43,000
 možda da imalo ime,

206
00:07:43,000 --> 00:07:44,000
 promijenim.

207
00:07:44,000 --> 00:07:45,000
 Ne da promijenim,

208
00:07:45,000 --> 00:07:46,000
 nego jedna sugestija,

209
00:07:46,000 --> 00:07:47,000
 tako,

210
00:07:47,000 --> 00:07:48,000
 vidjet ćete,

211
00:07:48,000 --> 00:07:49,000
 eto,

212
00:07:49,000 --> 00:07:50,000
 neću da ćete otkrivati

213
00:07:50,000 --> 00:07:51,000
 kao budete čitali,

214
00:07:51,000 --> 00:07:52,000
 neki poticaj

215
00:07:52,000 --> 00:07:53,000
 da bude

216
00:07:53,000 --> 00:07:55,000
 za taj karizmanski pokrit.

217
00:07:55,000 --> 00:07:56,000
 Znači,

218
00:07:56,000 --> 00:07:57,000
 Dug svijeti,

219
00:07:57,000 --> 00:07:59,000
 to su darovi očitovanja,

220
00:07:59,000 --> 00:08:00,000
 manifestacije.

221
00:08:00,000 --> 00:08:02,000
 Kad Dug svijeti dijeluje,

222
00:08:02,000 --> 00:08:03,000
 čuje se,

223
00:08:03,000 --> 00:08:04,000
 vidi se,

224
00:08:04,000 --> 00:08:05,000
 govori jesima,

225
00:08:05,000 --> 00:08:06,000
 čudesa,

226
00:08:06,000 --> 00:08:07,000
 i tako je Dug svijeti,

227
00:08:07,000 --> 00:08:08,000
 tako dijeluje,

228
00:08:08,000 --> 00:08:09,000
 neka tiho,

229
00:08:09,000 --> 00:08:10,000
 neka glasnije.

230
00:08:10,000 --> 00:08:12,000
 Sin traži da služimo,

231
00:08:12,000 --> 00:08:13,000
 po tim službama koje imamo,

232
00:08:13,000 --> 00:08:15,000
 oda se beske da dijelujemo,

233
00:08:15,000 --> 00:08:17,000
 da je na te talente darove.

234
00:08:17,000 --> 00:08:18,000
 Evo, to je važno,

235
00:08:18,000 --> 00:08:19,000
 da budemo svjesni.

236
00:08:19,000 --> 00:08:20,000
 I onda sam došao još,

237
00:08:20,000 --> 00:08:23,000
 razmišljajući o tim darovima,

238
00:08:23,000 --> 00:08:24,000
 a šta,

239
00:08:24,000 --> 00:08:25,000
 patnja,

240
00:08:25,000 --> 00:08:26,000
 trpjenje,

241
00:08:26,000 --> 00:08:27,000
 ne samo karizme,

242
00:08:27,000 --> 00:08:29,000
 stavljenje Boga,

243
00:08:29,000 --> 00:08:30,000
 onda sam došao i do

244
00:08:30,000 --> 00:08:32,000
 tog zaključka,

245
00:08:32,000 --> 00:08:34,000
 da je i mistični dio crkve,

246
00:08:34,000 --> 00:08:35,000
 i karizmanski,

247
00:08:35,000 --> 00:08:36,000
 zajedno.

248
00:08:36,000 --> 00:08:38,000
 Mistični znači biti pobjedan

249
00:08:38,000 --> 00:08:39,000
 s gospodinom.

250
00:08:39,000 --> 00:08:40,000
 E, vidite,

251
00:08:40,000 --> 00:08:41,000
 kada je Marko,

252
00:08:41,000 --> 00:08:42,000
 evanđelist,

253
00:08:42,000 --> 00:08:43,000
 govori,

254
00:08:43,000 --> 00:08:45,000
 zašto Isus ustanovio

255
00:08:45,000 --> 00:08:46,000
 o dvanestorcu.

256
00:08:46,000 --> 00:08:48,000
 kaže prvo,

257
00:08:48,000 --> 00:08:50,000
 da budu s njim,

258
00:08:50,000 --> 00:08:51,000
 pa onda kaže,

259
00:08:51,000 --> 00:08:52,000
 da ih šalje,

260
00:08:52,000 --> 00:08:55,000
 propovedati evanđelje,

261
00:08:55,000 --> 00:08:57,000
 navješajte evanđelje svima,

262
00:08:57,000 --> 00:08:58,000
 liječiti bolesne,

263
00:08:58,000 --> 00:09:00,000
 izgomiti zloduhe.

264
00:09:00,000 --> 00:09:02,000
 A prvo da budu s njim.

265
00:09:02,000 --> 00:09:03,000
 E, taj dio,

266
00:09:03,000 --> 00:09:05,000
 biti s gospodinom,

267
00:09:05,000 --> 00:09:07,000
 to je ta osobna molitva,

268
00:09:07,000 --> 00:09:09,000
 zajednička molitva,

269
00:09:09,000 --> 00:09:10,000
 biti s gospodinom,

270
00:09:10,000 --> 00:09:12,000
 biti uz gospodina,

271
00:09:12,000 --> 00:09:13,000
 uz jaslica,

272
00:09:13,000 --> 00:09:15,000
 uz križ,

273
00:09:15,000 --> 00:09:16,000
 biti s gospodinom,

274
00:09:16,000 --> 00:09:18,000
 tu se radja ta mistika,

275
00:09:18,000 --> 00:09:19,000
 to je škola života,

276
00:09:19,000 --> 00:09:21,000
 nasljenja Krista,

277
00:09:21,000 --> 00:09:23,000
 i onda kad to dobijemo,

278
00:09:23,000 --> 00:09:25,000
 darove od njega i pomoć,

279
00:09:25,000 --> 00:09:27,000
 onda nas Isus šalje,

280
00:09:27,000 --> 00:09:30,000
 da aktivno širimo evanđelje,

281
00:09:30,000 --> 00:09:31,000
 možda propovedamo na glas,

282
00:09:31,000 --> 00:09:33,000
 ili pišemo knjige,

283
00:09:33,000 --> 00:09:34,000
 propovedamo na radu,

284
00:09:34,000 --> 00:09:35,000
 ili pjevamo,

285
00:09:35,000 --> 00:09:37,000
 na bilo koji način.

286
00:09:37,000 --> 00:09:39,000
 Ali da bi smo to mogli uspješno raditi,

287
00:09:39,000 --> 00:09:43,000
 moramo ići prvo u školu,

288
00:09:43,000 --> 00:09:44,000
 kod gospodina.

289
00:09:44,000 --> 00:09:46,000
 E tu se razvija ta mistika,

290
00:09:46,000 --> 00:09:48,000
 povlačimo se.

291
00:09:48,000 --> 00:09:50,000
 Tako su i prvi pustinjaci,

292
00:09:50,000 --> 00:09:52,000
 bježali od svijeta,

293
00:09:52,000 --> 00:09:54,000
 da bi bili s gospodini u svijetu,

294
00:09:54,000 --> 00:09:56,000
 sveć izgubio duh hršćanstva,

295
00:09:56,000 --> 00:09:58,000
 i kad su oni bili napunjeni

296
00:09:58,000 --> 00:10:00,000
 duha svijetog snage,

297
00:10:00,000 --> 00:10:03,000
 onda je Bog nima slao ljude.

298
00:10:03,000 --> 00:10:04,000
 Onda su oni propovedali

299
00:10:04,000 --> 00:10:05,000
 svijetni antropus.

300
00:10:05,000 --> 00:10:08,000
 Tako je naš otac Franjo.

301
00:10:08,000 --> 00:10:10,000
 On je isto se povukao,

302
00:10:10,000 --> 00:10:12,000
 bio s gospodinom,

303
00:10:12,000 --> 00:10:13,000
 tražio se,

304
00:10:13,000 --> 00:10:16,000
 i onda kad je dobio što je tražio

305
00:10:16,000 --> 00:10:17,000
 i prepozvao se,

306
00:10:17,000 --> 00:10:20,000
 onda ga je Bog slao da ide u svijet,

307
00:10:20,000 --> 00:10:21,000
 propovedati evanđelje.

308
00:10:21,000 --> 00:10:23,000
 a onda je Franjo bio mudar,

309
00:10:23,000 --> 00:10:24,000
 kaže,

310
00:10:24,000 --> 00:10:26,000
 braća se moraju povremeno,

311
00:10:26,000 --> 00:10:27,000
 povlačiti u samoću,

312
00:10:27,000 --> 00:10:29,000
 skupiti snage i jakosti,

313
00:10:29,000 --> 00:10:32,000
 da bi onda mogli ići propovedati.

314
00:10:32,000 --> 00:10:33,000
 Evo,

315
00:10:33,000 --> 00:10:34,000
 braćaj i sestri,

316
00:10:34,000 --> 00:10:36,000
 još bi ovako napomenuo

317
00:10:36,000 --> 00:10:38,000
 da se ne bojite

318
00:10:38,000 --> 00:10:39,000
 kad zbog svijeti potakli,

319
00:10:39,000 --> 00:10:41,000
 a nešto radite.

320
00:10:41,000 --> 00:10:42,000
 Da sam Bog,

321
00:10:42,000 --> 00:10:43,000
 da im ja i ranije

322
00:10:43,000 --> 00:10:45,000
 počeo neke stvari raditi,

323
00:10:45,000 --> 00:10:47,000
 nego tek tamo

324
00:10:47,000 --> 00:10:48,000
 kad sam već bio svećenik,

325
00:10:48,000 --> 00:10:49,000
 sam 35,

326
00:10:49,000 --> 00:10:50,000
 8,

327
00:10:50,000 --> 00:10:51,000
 40 godina,

328
00:10:51,000 --> 00:10:54,000
 koliko sam sjećan se potica imao.

329
00:10:54,000 --> 00:10:55,000
 Evo i kroz srednju školu,

330
00:10:55,000 --> 00:10:56,000
 kao sam mištarac,

331
00:10:56,000 --> 00:10:57,000
 pa kao bogosom,

332
00:10:57,000 --> 00:10:59,000
 pa kao mladi svećenik,

333
00:10:59,000 --> 00:11:00,000
 sve nekako,

334
00:11:00,000 --> 00:11:01,000
 ono,

335
00:11:01,000 --> 00:11:02,000
 odbijanje,

336
00:11:02,000 --> 00:11:03,000
 pa nije to za mene,

337
00:11:03,000 --> 00:11:04,000
 pa mnogo ja to,

338
00:11:04,000 --> 00:11:06,000
 nisam ni razumio mnoge stvari,

339
00:11:06,000 --> 00:11:08,000
 a uglavnom bio bojazan

340
00:11:08,000 --> 00:11:09,000
 i taj strah,

341
00:11:09,000 --> 00:11:10,000
 šta će koreći?

342
00:11:10,000 --> 00:11:12,000
 Šta će koreći?

343
00:11:12,000 --> 00:11:14,000
 Onda se mi nekako to građujemo,

344
00:11:14,000 --> 00:11:16,000
 bojimo se i tako.

345
00:11:16,000 --> 00:11:18,000
 Ne bojite se,

346
00:11:18,000 --> 00:11:19,000
 odazovite se,

347
00:11:19,000 --> 00:11:20,000
 Bog će vas uvijek potaknuti,

348
00:11:20,000 --> 00:11:21,000
 naćete svoje mjesto

349
00:11:21,000 --> 00:11:23,000
 u izgradnje crkve.

350
00:11:23,000 --> 00:11:25,000
 Samo budite ponizi i hrabri

351
00:11:25,000 --> 00:11:27,000
 i gospodin će krenite.

352
00:11:27,000 --> 00:11:28,000
 Evo, iza mene,

353
00:11:28,000 --> 00:11:30,000
 ovdje imate puno ovi slika,

354
00:11:30,000 --> 00:11:31,000
 lijepi o svijetom Franji,

355
00:11:31,000 --> 00:11:32,000
 zamislite,

356
00:11:32,000 --> 00:11:33,000
 recimo,

357
00:11:33,000 --> 00:11:34,000
 madnesom svijet Franji,

358
00:11:34,000 --> 00:11:36,000
 uzmite i Bibliju,

359
00:11:36,000 --> 00:11:38,000
 da ljudi nisu slušali potice

360
00:11:38,000 --> 00:11:39,000
 duha svijetoga,

361
00:11:39,000 --> 00:11:41,000
 da Petar nije onaj san

362
00:11:41,000 --> 00:11:43,000
 onim životnjama,

363
00:11:43,000 --> 00:11:44,000
 onoj posudi,

364
00:11:44,000 --> 00:11:45,000
 razumio kako treba,

365
00:11:45,000 --> 00:11:46,000
 nikad ne bi otvorio

366
00:11:46,000 --> 00:11:48,000
 vrata Poganma.

367
00:11:48,000 --> 00:11:49,000
 On je otvorio vrata Poganma u crkvu,

368
00:11:49,000 --> 00:11:50,000
 nije,

369
00:11:50,000 --> 00:11:51,000
 Pao je,

370
00:11:51,000 --> 00:11:52,000
 Pao je kasnije da šao.

371
00:11:52,000 --> 00:11:54,000
 San, obični san,

372
00:11:54,000 --> 00:11:55,000
 ali nadaktno duha svijeta.

373
00:11:55,000 --> 00:11:56,000
 Vidite kako,

374
00:11:56,000 --> 00:11:57,000
 preko snova,

375
00:11:57,000 --> 00:11:58,000
 Bog minja crkvu,

376
00:11:58,000 --> 00:12:00,000
 poslije promijenio pravac svijeta.

377
00:12:00,000 --> 00:12:02,000
 Znate kako je otšao kod Kornelija,

378
00:12:02,000 --> 00:12:04,000
 orijinskog vojnika,

379
00:12:04,000 --> 00:12:06,000
 i naviješio evanđelje,

380
00:12:06,000 --> 00:12:07,000
 i kršćo ih.

381
00:12:07,000 --> 00:12:09,000
 Onda drugi tamo napali ga,

382
00:12:09,000 --> 00:12:10,000
 kućeš tići kod Poganma,

383
00:12:10,000 --> 00:12:11,000
 kako će ga prijemiti.

384
00:12:11,000 --> 00:12:12,000
 On kao,

385
00:12:12,000 --> 00:12:13,000
 nisam ja,

386
00:12:13,000 --> 00:12:14,000
 ti u dug svijeti sišu.

387
00:12:14,000 --> 00:12:16,000
 A prije toga san.

388
00:12:16,000 --> 00:12:18,000
 Ili mnogi drugi,

389
00:12:18,000 --> 00:12:19,000
 evo svijeti Franju,

390
00:12:19,000 --> 00:12:20,000
 isto imamo snove,

391
00:12:20,000 --> 00:12:21,000
 Dom Bosko,

392
00:12:21,000 --> 00:12:22,000
 a zamislite evo,

393
00:12:22,000 --> 00:12:23,000
 svijeti Franju,

394
00:12:23,000 --> 00:12:25,000
 kako nadahnut,

395
00:12:25,000 --> 00:12:27,000
 u ono vrijeme,

396
00:12:27,000 --> 00:12:28,000
 palo mu na pamet,

397
00:12:28,000 --> 00:12:31,000
 da slavi svijetom mislu u štali.

398
00:12:31,000 --> 00:12:33,000
 Pogotovo u to vrijeme,

399
00:12:33,000 --> 00:12:35,000
 postoje propisi gdje se misla slavi.

400
00:12:35,000 --> 00:12:37,000
 On dobio nadahnuće,

401
00:12:37,000 --> 00:12:40,000
 i želi slaviti svijetom mislu u štali.

402
00:12:40,000 --> 00:12:42,000
 Ljudi su poslušali,

403
00:12:42,000 --> 00:12:44,000
 ja mislim su mnogi svećini tada

404
00:12:44,000 --> 00:12:45,000
 ga lamli, vikali,

405
00:12:45,000 --> 00:12:47,000
 šta mu je normalan,

406
00:12:47,000 --> 00:12:49,000
 gdje će sve to mislu slavi tu štali.

407
00:12:49,000 --> 00:12:50,000
 Ali on je poslušao,

408
00:12:50,000 --> 00:12:53,000
 i vidite šta se stvorilo u crkvi,

409
00:12:53,000 --> 00:12:54,000
 ono Franjovačko,

410
00:12:54,000 --> 00:12:56,000
 jaslice, misa, blizina,

411
00:12:56,000 --> 00:12:57,000
 i bez toga,

412
00:12:57,000 --> 00:12:59,000
 ono što je bilo samo Franjovačko,

413
00:12:59,000 --> 00:13:01,000
 frajno postalo je dio crkve.

414
00:13:01,000 --> 00:13:04,000
 Tako sve karizme treba postati dio crkve.

415
00:13:04,000 --> 00:13:05,000
 Ili,

416
00:13:05,000 --> 00:13:08,000
 častio je Isusa raspio toga put križa,

417
00:13:08,000 --> 00:13:09,000
 na laverni,

418
00:13:09,000 --> 00:13:11,000
 svaki dan su frate slavili.

419
00:13:11,000 --> 00:13:13,000
 I to je postalo sada,

420
00:13:13,000 --> 00:13:15,000
 posto je u svim crkvama,

421
00:13:15,000 --> 00:13:16,000
 katočkim se nalaze do duše,

422
00:13:16,000 --> 00:13:18,000
 Njemačka već skidaju,

423
00:13:18,000 --> 00:13:19,000
 u mnogim crkva nema.

424
00:13:19,000 --> 00:13:22,000
 Sveti je Franjov dobio to nadahnuće.

425
00:13:22,000 --> 00:13:23,000
 I onda je postalo to,

426
00:13:23,000 --> 00:13:25,000
 to je ta njegova karizma bila,

427
00:13:25,000 --> 00:13:27,000
 razmatrao muku Hristo,

428
00:13:27,000 --> 00:13:28,000
 dobio rane.

429
00:13:28,000 --> 00:13:30,000
 i tako isto mnoge stvari.

430
00:13:30,000 --> 00:13:31,000
 Ili, uzmite ovo,

431
00:13:31,000 --> 00:13:33,000
 otku njemu pravo,

432
00:13:33,000 --> 00:13:35,000
 da on primi neku djevojku,

433
00:13:35,000 --> 00:13:36,000
 tamo klaru,

434
00:13:36,000 --> 00:13:38,000
 koja pobjega od kuće,

435
00:13:38,000 --> 00:13:40,000
 i sada je tamo odrezao koso,

436
00:13:40,000 --> 00:13:42,000
 primio je u redovnice.

437
00:13:42,000 --> 00:13:44,000
 niti on frata,

438
00:13:44,000 --> 00:13:45,000
 niti svećanik,

439
00:13:45,000 --> 00:13:46,000
 ono se nije svećanik,

440
00:13:46,000 --> 00:13:47,000
 džakon, biskup,

441
00:13:47,000 --> 00:13:48,000
 koje on,

442
00:13:48,000 --> 00:13:49,000
 otkudno to pravo,

443
00:13:49,000 --> 00:13:51,000
 da primi u red nekoga.

444
00:13:51,000 --> 00:13:53,000
 A duše ti ga nadahnu.

445
00:13:53,000 --> 00:13:56,000
 U vidite taj kontekst,

446
00:13:56,000 --> 00:13:58,000
 sad kad bi neko od vas,

447
00:13:58,000 --> 00:13:59,000
 nekoga,

448
00:13:59,000 --> 00:14:01,000
 neku djevoju ko će ići,

449
00:14:01,000 --> 00:14:03,000
 pozvijesati da je neko primi,

450
00:14:03,000 --> 00:14:04,000
 odrežio kose,

451
00:14:04,000 --> 00:14:06,000
 da pred njim položi zavit,

452
00:14:06,000 --> 00:14:07,000
 rekao,

453
00:14:07,000 --> 00:14:08,000
 otkud to bi to pravo,

454
00:14:08,000 --> 00:14:09,000
 nemaš ti to.

455
00:14:09,000 --> 00:14:10,000
 Tako svi ti, Franju,

456
00:14:10,000 --> 00:14:12,000
 radi sa svetom klarom.

457
00:14:12,000 --> 00:14:13,000
 E, te to su sve stvari,

458
00:14:13,000 --> 00:14:15,000
 kako Duh Sveti djeluje

459
00:14:15,000 --> 00:14:17,000
 i kako se onda to razvija

460
00:14:17,000 --> 00:14:18,000
 malo po malo.

461
00:14:18,000 --> 00:14:19,000
 Evo tako,

462
00:14:19,000 --> 00:14:21,000
 budite otvoreni,

463
00:14:21,000 --> 00:14:23,000
 poticaj Duha Svetoga,

464
00:14:23,000 --> 00:14:24,000
 znamo,

465
00:14:24,000 --> 00:14:27,000
 da je Bog još preko proroka Velea rekao

466
00:14:27,000 --> 00:14:29,000
 da će svi,

467
00:14:29,000 --> 00:14:31,000
 i stari, i madi, i muška, i žensko,

468
00:14:31,000 --> 00:14:33,000
 imat ćemo proroštva,

469
00:14:33,000 --> 00:14:34,000
 tako,

470
00:14:34,000 --> 00:14:35,000
 imat ćemo vizije,

471
00:14:35,000 --> 00:14:37,000
 i snove.

472
00:14:37,000 --> 00:14:39,000
 Bog nam prilazi na onaj način

473
00:14:39,000 --> 00:14:40,000
 koji je nama prikladan.

474
00:14:40,000 --> 00:14:42,000
 Svetom Jospo je preko snova govorio.

475
00:14:42,000 --> 00:14:45,000
 Možda da vam je govorio preko proroštva direktno,

476
00:14:45,000 --> 00:14:47,000
 on bi se uplašio,

477
00:14:47,000 --> 00:14:48,000
 još bi više poslušao,

478
00:14:48,000 --> 00:14:50,000
 ovako je preko snova,

479
00:14:50,000 --> 00:14:51,000
 mogo je odbiti,

480
00:14:51,000 --> 00:14:52,000
 ali bio je poslušan i tako.

481
00:14:52,000 --> 00:14:54,000
 Neko preko snova govori,

482
00:14:54,000 --> 00:14:55,000
 neko preko vizija,

483
00:14:55,000 --> 00:14:57,000
 neko preko proroštva.

484
00:14:57,000 --> 00:14:59,000
 Samo to treba, naravno,

485
00:14:59,000 --> 00:15:00,000
 provjeravati.

486
00:15:00,000 --> 00:15:02,000
 Primijetio sam

487
00:15:02,000 --> 00:15:05,000
 da je naša ljudska,

488
00:15:05,000 --> 00:15:07,000
 ovako skonost,

489
00:15:07,000 --> 00:15:09,000
 kad nešto volimo,

490
00:15:09,000 --> 00:15:11,000
 kad su karizmatici te stvari,

491
00:15:11,000 --> 00:15:13,000
 i čim neko kaže ima vizije,

492
00:15:13,000 --> 00:15:14,000
 mi ima kaže,

493
00:15:14,000 --> 00:15:15,000
 tako je, bravo,

494
00:15:15,000 --> 00:15:16,000
 i hvalimo se.

495
00:15:16,000 --> 00:15:18,000
 ili ako smo proti toga,

496
00:15:18,000 --> 00:15:19,000
 odmah odbijamo.

497
00:15:19,000 --> 00:15:20,000
 Ne volja ni jedan,

498
00:15:20,000 --> 00:15:21,000
 ni drugi stav.

499
00:15:21,000 --> 00:15:23,000
 Kaže Sveti Pavel,

500
00:15:23,000 --> 00:15:25,000
 svada nadahnuća,

501
00:15:25,000 --> 00:15:26,000
 i kod sebe,

502
00:15:26,000 --> 00:15:27,000
 i kod drugi,

503
00:15:27,000 --> 00:15:28,000
 treba provjeravati.

504
00:15:28,000 --> 00:15:30,000
 A to je najteže.

505
00:15:30,000 --> 00:15:32,000
 Kad ispituješ džak,

506
00:15:32,000 --> 00:15:34,000
 ili gledaš onu zadaću,

507
00:15:34,000 --> 00:15:35,000
 meni,

508
00:15:35,000 --> 00:15:37,000
 odmah kad pogledam,

509
00:15:37,000 --> 00:15:38,000
 iz Englesko,

510
00:15:38,000 --> 00:15:39,000
 recimo na brzinu,

511
00:15:39,000 --> 00:15:40,000
 mogu pogledati,

512
00:15:40,000 --> 00:15:40,000
 reći,

513
00:15:40,000 --> 00:15:41,000
 ovo je dobar džak,

514
00:15:41,000 --> 00:15:42,000
 odmah dat pet,

515
00:15:42,000 --> 00:15:43,000
 ne moram ni gledati.

516
00:15:43,000 --> 00:15:44,000
 Ili, ako ga ne volim,

517
00:15:44,000 --> 00:15:46,000
 reći, ništa ne volja,

518
00:15:46,000 --> 00:15:48,000
 i ocijen ga negativno.

519
00:15:48,000 --> 00:15:50,000
 Treba uzeti detalje,

520
00:15:50,000 --> 00:15:51,000
 analizirati.

521
00:15:51,000 --> 00:15:52,000
 E tu se traži od nas,

522
00:15:52,000 --> 00:15:53,000
 da darove,

523
00:15:53,000 --> 00:15:55,000
 duha Svetoga,

524
00:15:55,000 --> 00:15:56,000
 provjeravamo,

525
00:15:56,000 --> 00:15:57,000
 nadahnuća.

526
00:15:57,000 --> 00:16:00,000
 To će viradno i neki drugi govoriti.

527
00:16:00,000 --> 00:16:01,000
 Nadahnuće,

528
00:16:01,000 --> 00:16:04,000
 može doći iz naše posvijeste,

529
00:16:04,000 --> 00:16:05,000
 naše želje,

530
00:16:05,000 --> 00:16:06,000
 i mi onda to proglasimo,

531
00:16:06,000 --> 00:16:07,000
 a to Boži,

532
00:16:07,000 --> 00:16:08,000
 a nije Boži.

533
00:16:08,000 --> 00:16:11,000
 Može doći od duha Svetoga,

534
00:16:11,000 --> 00:16:13,000
 a mi mislimo da je od ljudi,

535
00:16:13,000 --> 00:16:14,000
 pa ne poslušamo.

536
00:16:14,000 --> 00:16:15,000
 I naravno,

537
00:16:15,000 --> 00:16:17,000
 može doći od zloduha.

538
00:16:17,000 --> 00:16:19,000
 I zloduha nam može potakni,

539
00:16:19,000 --> 00:16:20,000
 mislim od duha Svetoga,

540
00:16:20,000 --> 00:16:21,000
 pa poslušamo naopak.

541
00:16:21,000 --> 00:16:24,000
 E tu se moramo u poniznosti,

542
00:16:24,000 --> 00:16:25,000
 učiti cijeli život,

543
00:16:25,000 --> 00:16:27,000
 i ta nadahnuća,

544
00:16:27,000 --> 00:16:28,000
 provjeravati.

545
00:16:28,000 --> 00:16:30,000
 kao što je kod Svetog Franje,

546
00:16:30,000 --> 00:16:32,000
 kad imamo te svoje nadahnuća,

547
00:16:32,000 --> 00:16:34,000
 provjeravala crkva,

548
00:16:34,000 --> 00:16:36,000
 i kad je bilo da je to ispravno,

549
00:16:36,000 --> 00:16:37,000
 to je prihvaćeno u crkvi,

550
00:16:37,000 --> 00:16:39,000
 i postalo opće dobro.

551
00:16:39,000 --> 00:16:40,000
 Evo,

552
00:16:40,000 --> 00:16:41,000
 budimo dakle ponizi,

553
00:16:41,000 --> 00:16:42,000
 strpljivi,

554
00:16:42,000 --> 00:16:45,000
 slušajmo riješ Božju,

555
00:16:45,000 --> 00:16:47,000
 budimo otvoreni poticajem duha Svetoga,

556
00:16:47,000 --> 00:16:49,000
 ali provjerajmo,

557
00:16:49,000 --> 00:16:50,000
 budimo hrabri,

558
00:16:50,000 --> 00:16:53,000
 nemojmo se obazirati što će koreć,

559
00:16:53,000 --> 00:16:54,000
 poštujemo tuđe mišljenje,

560
00:16:54,000 --> 00:16:56,000
 a više se bojimo Boga,

561
00:16:56,000 --> 00:16:57,000
 i slušamo njega,

562
00:16:57,000 --> 00:17:00,000
 i Bog će nam dati svoj blagoslov.

563
00:17:00,000 --> 00:17:01,000
 Evo neka, gospodini,

564
00:17:01,000 --> 00:17:03,000
 preko ovog našeg susreta,

565
00:17:03,000 --> 00:17:04,000
 ovdje ovih dana,

566
00:17:04,000 --> 00:17:05,000
 u Mostaru,

567
00:17:05,000 --> 00:17:08,000
 sve nas ojači u tom zajedništu,

568
00:17:08,000 --> 00:17:10,000
 zajedništvo Duh Sveti,

569
00:17:10,000 --> 00:17:12,000
 onaj koji stvori zajedno zloduh,

570
00:17:12,000 --> 00:17:13,000
 dijabolos,

571
00:17:13,000 --> 00:17:14,000
 onaj koji razdvaja.

572
00:17:14,000 --> 00:17:18,000
 Da postanemo jedna srcena duša,

573
00:17:18,000 --> 00:17:21,000
 da budemo kvasa svoga svijeta,

574
00:17:21,000 --> 00:17:22,000
 kvasa je malo,

575
00:17:22,000 --> 00:17:25,000
 a onda i da je uz kvasa tijesla.

576
00:17:25,000 --> 00:17:27,000
 Ne treba biti velika zajednica,

577
00:17:27,000 --> 00:17:30,000
 i u svijetu se smanje broj kršćanostog katolika,

578
00:17:30,000 --> 00:17:33,000
 ali imamo silu, snagu duha svijetoga,

579
00:17:33,000 --> 00:17:34,000
 ako smo i mali,

580
00:17:34,000 --> 00:17:36,000
 možemo mijenjati svijet.

581
00:17:36,000 --> 00:17:40,000
 Ne dajte da svijet i mentalitet vas mijenja,

582
00:17:40,000 --> 00:17:41,000
 nego vi,

583
00:17:41,000 --> 00:17:43,000
 nadaknuti duhovom svijetim,

584
00:17:43,000 --> 00:17:45,000
 potaknuti primjerom svijetaca

585
00:17:45,000 --> 00:17:47,000
 i Boželjice Marije,

586
00:17:47,000 --> 00:17:48,000
 mijenjajte svijet,

587
00:17:48,000 --> 00:17:50,000
 odnosno mijenjamo svijet.

588
00:17:50,000 --> 00:17:52,000
 Ne možemo bez duha svijetoga,

589
00:17:52,000 --> 00:17:54,000
 bez njegovih darova karizmi,

590
00:17:54,000 --> 00:17:56,000
 ne možemo,

591
00:17:56,000 --> 00:17:57,000
 moramo i podijediti,

592
00:17:57,000 --> 00:17:58,000
 moliti,

593
00:17:58,000 --> 00:17:59,000
 prihvatiti,

594
00:17:59,000 --> 00:18:00,000
 cijeniti,

595
00:18:00,000 --> 00:18:01,000
 poštivati,

596
00:18:01,000 --> 00:18:02,000
 poštivati crkvu,

597
00:18:02,000 --> 00:18:04,000
 i crkva je karizmanska,

598
00:18:04,000 --> 00:18:05,000
 to je povezano,

599
00:18:05,000 --> 00:18:08,000
 baš tu preporučujem i svećanicima,

600
00:18:08,000 --> 00:18:09,000
 da,

601
00:18:09,000 --> 00:18:11,000
 ima opisano je,

602
00:18:11,000 --> 00:18:12,000
 ona jovenistite,

603
00:18:12,000 --> 00:18:13,000
 teklizija,

604
00:18:13,000 --> 00:18:14,000
 crkva se pomađuje,

605
00:18:14,000 --> 00:18:15,000
 gdje se gori,

606
00:18:15,000 --> 00:18:17,000
 odnosu ti karizmanski,

607
00:18:17,000 --> 00:18:18,000
 darova i hierarhijski,

608
00:18:18,000 --> 00:18:20,000
 da su oni u harmoniji,

609
00:18:20,000 --> 00:18:21,000
 u skladu,

610
00:18:21,000 --> 00:18:23,000
 kao što kao svijetofranje bilo.

611
00:18:23,000 --> 00:18:26,000
 Njegovo je bila poticaj duha svijetoga,

612
00:18:26,000 --> 00:18:28,000
 da slavi jasnice i to,

613
00:18:28,000 --> 00:18:29,000
 kasnije je to postalo,

614
00:18:29,000 --> 00:18:31,000
 kao institucionalno u crkvi,

615
00:18:31,000 --> 00:18:32,000
 spozna to sve,

616
00:18:32,000 --> 00:18:33,000
 crkva je to prihvatila.

617
00:18:33,000 --> 00:18:34,000
 Evo,

618
00:18:34,000 --> 00:18:36,000
 tako nekako se povežimo,

619
00:18:36,000 --> 00:18:37,000
 učimo se od gospe,

620
00:18:37,000 --> 00:18:39,000
 nju uslušajmo,

621
00:18:39,000 --> 00:18:41,000
 ona nas poziva na post molitvu,

622
00:18:41,000 --> 00:18:42,000
 meditaciju,

623
00:18:42,000 --> 00:18:44,000
 u jednu ruku uzimo krunicu,

624
00:18:44,000 --> 00:18:46,000
 u drugu Bibliju

625
00:18:46,000 --> 00:18:47,000
 i polako,

626
00:18:47,000 --> 00:18:48,000
 kroz ovaj život,

627
00:18:48,000 --> 00:18:50,000
 idimo hrabro svjedočimo,

628
00:18:50,000 --> 00:18:51,000
 Božju ljubav,

629
00:18:51,000 --> 00:18:53,000
 budimo sol zemi

630
00:18:53,000 --> 00:18:55,000
 i budimo svjetlo svijetu.

631
00:18:55,000 --> 00:18:56,000
 Amen.

